Inter Milan have officially completed the signing of playmaker, Christian Eriksen from Tottenham Hotspur. Eriksen will wear the number 24 shirt at Inter Milan. Inter Milan made this known in a statement on their official website on Tuesday. The statement read: “MILAN – After officially joining the Nerazzurri, Christian Eriksen has chosen the number that he’ll wear during his Inter adventure: the number 24! “It will soon be possible to buy the Danish midfielder’s shirt from store.inter.it, the Inter Store Milano and the San Siro store.”